# IP-sensitive: ALL plan documents kept local-only.  The crate
# sources (hymeko_nagare/, hymeko_*/) remain tracked — they're
# implementation, less legible as a research idea than the plan
# .tex/.tikz/.mmd/.pdf set.  Plans (Nagare and all others) carry
# the forward-looking IP and are excluded pending a Zenodo /
# defensive-publication strategy.  Do NOT relax this without explicit
# IP-strategy review (co-author Csapó for Nagare-line work).
/docs/plans/
/docs/notes/2026-05-18-task-execution-as-hsmm.md

